name: Accelerate Diversified Credit Income Fund
longDescription: Accelerate Diversified Credit Income Fund seeks to deliver exposure to alternative sources of income compared to traditional fixed income funds by focusing on, but not limited to, the private credit, direct lending, asset-backed and mortgage-backed securities market. The Accelerate Diversified Credit Income Fund is a highyield income solution focused on diversification and capital preservation in private credit.
